  "title": "Electrical Drafter",
  "description": "<h3>Job Description</h3><p>We are looking for a responsible and detail-oriented <strong>Electrical / Electronics Draughtsman</strong> to support our project and engineering team. The candidate will prepare electrical drawings, layouts, and technical documentation for building and system installations.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Prepare electrical and electronics drawings using <strong>AutoCAD</strong> (or similar software)</p></li><li><p>Produce layout drawings, single line diagrams, schematic drawings, and as-built drawings</p></li><li><p>Assist engineers in preparing shop drawings and submission drawings</p></li><li><p>Update drawings according to site conditions and consultant comments</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with project, site, and engineering teams</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper documentation and drawing records</p></li><li><p>Any other duties related to drafting support as assigned</p></li></ul>",
