    "description": "<p>Y&amp;T Aircon Engineering Pte Ltd.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The company business activities including general contracting for building works, as well as repair of refrigerating, air-conditioning and ventilating machinery and equipment . Provide air-conditioning engineering services including installation, servicing and maintenance of air-conditioning and ventilation systems (for commercial / industrial / building works).<br>\n<br>\nAs a general contractor for building construction (and major upgrading works) with specialization in HVAC/M&amp;E systems, the company is well-versed in site work, system integration, and working with building services teams. <br>\n<br>\nOur team of technicians and engineers work across HVAC systems , split units, cassette ceilings, ducted systems, chiller / air-handler units (depending on project) and perform preventive maintenance, troubleshooting, repair and installation.</p>",
